Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看都看不厭
